12 years ago, we started talking (again) around this time. As teenagers, we never thought, even in the wildest of our dreams, that this day would come (so soon). There have been ups and downs, numerous fights and arguments, distances, but there has also been immense happiness, laughter and boundless love. We’ve finally decided to love, laugh, fight, argue, play, cry, travel together for the rest of our lives 🧿❤️🥂
To what started as infatuation between two friends has now turned into a lifetime of commitment and craziness between two best friends!
#ApaarulInLove
